{"title":"nvm安装","uid":"53ac39e10789bec03d342be6b8491c75","slug":"nvm安装","date":"2023-10-20T08:42:11.000Z","updated":"2023-10-20T08:48:16.190Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/nvm安装.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<h3 id=\"nvm安装\"><a href=\"#nvm安装\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"nvm安装\"></a>nvm安装</h3><p>​\tnvm是node的版本管理工具，可以安装多个版本的node并切换，直接从官网安装node，进行npm install时经常出错（需要sudo），所以用nvm进行安装node</p>\n<ol>\n<li><p>卸载旧版本node、npm</p>\n<div class=\"language-shell\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">shell</span><pre class=\"shiki material-theme-palenight\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">brew</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">uninstall</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">node</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">sudo</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">rm</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">-rf</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">/usr/local/&#123;bin/&#123;node,npm&#125;,lib/node_modules/npm,lib/node,share/man/</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">*</span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">/node.</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">*</span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">&#125;</span></span></code></pre></div></li>\n<li><p>安装</p>\n<div class=\"language-shell\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">shell</span><pre class=\"shiki material-theme-palenight\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">git</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">clone</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">https://github.com/nvm-sh/nvm.git</span></span></code></pre></div></li>\n<li><p>配置环境</p>\n<div class=\"language-shell\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">shell</span><pre class=\"shiki material-theme-palenight\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #676E95; font-style: italic\"># vim ~/.zshrc</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span></code></pre></div><p>加上以下内容 </p>\n<div class=\"language-txt\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">txt</span><pre class=\"shiki material-theme-palenight\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">export NVM_DIR=&quot;$HOME/.nvm&quot;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">[ -s &quot;$NVM_DIR/nvm.sh&quot; ] &amp;&amp; \\. &quot;$NVM_DIR/nvm.sh&quot;  # This loads nvm</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">[ -s &quot;$NVM_DIR/bash_completion&quot; ] &amp;&amp; \\. &quot;$NVM_DIR/bash_completion&quot;  # This loads nvm bash_completion</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\"></span></span></code></pre></div><div class=\"language-shell\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">shell</span><pre class=\"shiki material-theme-palenight\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #82AAFF\">source</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">~/.zshrc</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">nvm</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">-v</span></span></code></pre></div></li>\n<li><p>设置淘宝镜像</p>\n<div class=\"language-shell\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">shell</span><pre class=\"shiki material-theme-palenight\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">NVM_NODEJS_ORG_MIRROR</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">=</span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">https://npm.taobao.org/mirrors/node</span></span></code></pre></div></li>\n<li><p>安装node</p>\n<div class=\"language-shell\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">shell</span><pre class=\"shiki material-theme-palenight\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #676E95; font-style: italic\">#查看node可安装版本</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">nvm</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">ls-remote</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #676E95; font-style: italic\">#安装v18.18.2 版本，也可以选你需要的版本</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">nvm</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">installl</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">v18.18.2</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #676E95; font-style: italic\">#切换，可以切换其他版本</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">nvm</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">use</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">v18.18.2</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span></code></pre></div></li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"node配置\"><a href=\"#node配置\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"node配置\"></a>node配置</h3><ol>\n<li><p>设置镜像</p>\n<div class=\"language-shell\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">shell</span><pre class=\"shiki material-theme-palenight\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #676E95; font-style: italic\"># 这个地址好像过期了，配置后不起加速作用</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #676E95; font-style: italic\"># npm config set registry https://registry.npm.taobao.org/</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #676E95; font-style: italic\">#用下面这个</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">npm</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">config</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">set</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">registry</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">https://registry.npmmirror.com/</span></span></code></pre></div></li>\n</ol>\n","text":"nvm安装​ nvm是node的版本管理工具，可以安装多个版本的node并切换，直接从官网安装node，进行npm install时经常出错（需要sudo），所...","permalink":"/post/nvm安装","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":979,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#nvm%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85\"><span class=\"toc-text\">nvm安装</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#node%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE\"><span class=\"toc-text\">node配置</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"Aurora","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"","link":"/","description":"","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"hidden":false,"prev_post":{},"next_post":{"title":"Hello World","uid":"b9663f58f18133b35bfe243f3e916a80","slug":"hello-world","date":"2023-10-20T08:20:55.238Z","updated":"2023-10-20T08:20:55.238Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/hello-world.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"text":"Welcome to Hexo! This is your very first post. Check documentation for more info..